      • INTERACTIVE_SUDO

        public static final SshConnectionType INTERACTIVE_SUDO
        An SSH connection that uses SCP to transfer files, to a Unix host. Uses SUDO, not been configured with NOPASSWD for all commands, to execute commands.

      • TUNNEL
